%N A014999 Inverse of 990th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A014999 Periodic with period length 990. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A014999 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A014999/b014999.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%H A014999 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 990.
